dfischer.utils

Class ApicaPMANetConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.ApicaPMANetConfig

  • public class ApicaPMANetConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Store and load configuration data about the network connection to an Apica Performance Monitoring Agent Controller (PMA).
